rows.label: qst702804_msg0002
rows.name:
Morumo impressed, really. Even in
midst of battle, have been admiring
way hero-hero-friends fight...

rows.label: qst702804_msg0004
rows.name:
No! Morumo never give up! Dream of
Morumo never come true by giving up!

rows.label: qst702804_msg0007
rows.name:
We have to stop him! He's going
to fall and get himself hurt!

rows.label: qst702804_msg0008
rows.name:
If he hurts himself, it's his
own dumb fault!

rows.label: qst702804_msg0010
rows.name:
Don't worry. He won't get far,
not on this scaffolding.

rows.label: qst702804_msg0011
rows.name:
I suppose we'll have to track him
as carefully as we can, then.

rows.label: qst702804_msg0012
rows.name:
Yeah? I'm not exactly seeing
a path ahead...

rows.label: qst702804_msg0013
rows.name: We could always leave you behind.

rows.label: qst702804_msg0014
rows.name:
What? That's not what I-
No one is leaving me behind!
